_xResult.title: Moonlight Maxi Dress
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made larger than life dress with short-sleeves
_xResult.longdesc:
Dark blue captures the eye immediately, pulling it into an unbreakable trance, on a dress as captivating as the night sky. The extra fabric used for this custom made maxi dress is overwhelming in the best ways. Simple and sophisticated, the scoop neck, short-sleeves and pure soft brushed cotton will have you dreaming and dancing the night away.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
